This paper deals with educational data mining and adaptive learning systems, which are typically associated with machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also proposes a new method for measuring similarity between educational items using performance data, which could be relevant to computational engineering (cs.CE) and computational linguistics (cs.CL). Finally, the paper focuses on K6 Math education, which falls under the category of educational technology (cs.EDU).
